51:29.430 --> 51:32.269
No, no, no, I'm good, home slice.

51:32.270 --> 51:33.479
Positive, bucco, because you were doing

51:33.480 --> 51:35.159
a lotta talking in there, hombre.

51:35.160 --> 51:36.929
Okay, look, Ed, I'm
running out of synonyms

51:36.930 --> 51:39.399
that guys call each other, so can we just?

51:39.400 --> 51:41.889
I knew you'd blink first, chico.

51:41.890 --> 51:43.190
You got a problem with me?

51:45.263 --> 51:47.019
Hey, I'm talking to you.

51:47.020 --> 51:48.193
Why do you care?

51:49.530 --> 51:51.579
You got to stop caring what people think

51:51.580 --> 51:54.529
about you, man, it'll
drive you nuts, all right.

51:54.530 --> 51:58.069
