51:58.070 --> 51:59.070
I'm not.

52:02.270 --> 52:06.379
Did your family really
lose money from what I did?

52:06.380 --> 52:07.380
No, man.

52:09.295 --> 52:10.403
No, no.

52:11.820 --> 52:13.859
I just made that up as part of the improve.

52:13.860 --> 52:15.699
I just was deep in the role.

52:15.700 --> 52:17.287
