the shit out of them?

52:24.080 --> 52:26.669
Oh, affirmative, kemo sabe.

52:26.670 --> 52:28.100
Good one, let's go.

52:29.133 --> 52:30.999
Hey, come here, come here.

52:31.000 --> 52:33.159
