53:20.750 --> 53:23.633
and I have too much pride to
drink straight from the bottle.

53:29.620 --> 53:30.893
Hey-o, guys.

53:32.820 --> 53:33.820
Come on in.

53:35.440 --> 53:36.970
Pour yourself a bowl of Jack.

53:39.237 --> 53:40.824
Yeesh.

53:53.789 --> 53:56.122
Should I pull the trigger?

